Q1 2017 Results

	View first quarter 2017 Financials and MD&A

	 

	 

	 

	 
 









HomeInvestors

	ARC is recognized as a top-tier oil and natural gas producer for the strength of its assets and management team. Our goal is to create value and provide superior, long-term returns to shareholders. This goal is realized through the development of large oil and natural gas pools. While growth has been an outcome, the focus for ARC is always “risk managed value creation”. 

	ARC has a history of proven performance. Since inception it has paid over 5 billion in total dividends and has provided over an 18 per cent annual return to shareholders.  ARC’s technical expertise in resource play development, combined with a disciplined approach to capital investment provides a strong base for continued value creation and sets the stage for profitable growth into the future.

	 

	 


